title: Remove Negative Labels | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Remove Negative Labels | Joel Osteen
description:
People may have placed negative labels on you in the past, but God calls you strong, talented and valuable. When you let go of the labels that have held you back, God will help you become everything you were created to be. 


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
